<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-61-1222 </DOCNO><TEXT>A brief review is given of the problems which energy efficient investmentthrough third party financing has encountered in the European Communityand in particular the FRG. The two types of credit which emerge fromthe risk assessment of the financial institutions, particularly banks,are described. (U.K.).</TEXT></DOC>